from keras import backend as K

def recall_m(y_true, y_pred):
        true_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true * y_pred, 0, 1)))
        possible_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true, 0, 1)))
        recall = true_positives / (possible_positives + K.epsilon())
        return recall

def precision_m(y_true, y_pred):
        true_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true * y_pred, 0, 1)))
        predicted_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_pred, 0, 1)))
        precision = true_positives / (predicted_positives + K.epsilon())
        return precision

def f1_m(y_true, y_pred):
    precision = precision_m(y_true, y_pred)
    recall = recall_m(y_true, y_pred)
    return 2*((precision*recall)/(precision+recall+K.epsilon()))

def dum(y_true,y_pred):
    true_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true * y_pred, 0, 1)))
    possible_positives = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true, 0, 1)))
    recall = true_positives / (possible_positives + K.epsilon())
    return recall

x = model.layers[-1].output


#model = Model(input = img, output = output_layer)

output5 = Dense(1, activation = 'sigmoid',name='AU12')(x)
output6 = Dense(1, activation = 'sigmoid',name='AU15')(x)
output7 = Dense(1, activation = 'sigmoid',name='AU20')(x)
output8 = Dense(1, activation = 'sigmoid',name='AU25')(x)
model = Model(img,[output1,output2,output3,output4,output5,output6,output7,output8])

In [12]:
def generator_wrapper(generator):
    for batch_x,batch_y in generator:
        yield (batch_x,[batch_y[:,i] for i in range(8)])

import tensorflow as tf
class fun(tf.keras.callbacks.Callback):
    def on_epoch_end(self, epoch, logs=None):
        
        
        tot_val_f1_m=((logs['val_AU1_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU2_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU4_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU6_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU12_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU15_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU20_f1_m'])+(logs['val_AU25_f1_m']))
        tot_f1_m=((logs['AU1_f1_m'])+(logs['AU2_f1_m'])+(logs['AU4_f1_m'])+(logs['AU6_f1_m'])+(logs['AU12_f1_m'])+(logs['AU15_f1_m'])+(logs['AU20_f1_m'])+(logs['AU25_f1_m']))
        tot_val_acc=((logs['val_AU1_acc'])+(logs['val_AU2_acc'])+(logs['val_AU4_acc'])+(logs['val_AU6_acc'])+(logs['val_AU12_acc'])+(logs['val_AU15_acc'])+(logs['val_AU20_acc'])+(logs['val_AU25_acc']))
        tot_acc=((logs['AU1_acc'])+(logs['AU2_acc'])+(logs['AU4_acc'])+(logs['AU6_acc'])+(logs['AU12_acc'])+(logs['AU15_acc'])+(logs['AU20_acc'])+(logs['AU25_acc']))
        
        print("Printing total_val_f1_m",tot_val_f1_m)
        logs['val_AU1_dum']=tot_val_f1_m
        print("Printing dumped val_AU1_dum",logs['val_AU1_dum'])
        
        print("Printing total_f1_m",tot_f1_m)
        logs['val_AU2_dum']=tot_f1_m
        print("Printing dumped val_AU2_dum",logs['val_AU2_dum'])
        
        print("Printing total_val_acc",tot_val_acc)
        logs['val_AU4_dum']=tot_val_acc
        print("Printing dumped val_AU4_dum",logs['val_AU4_dum'])
        
        print("Printing total_acc",tot_acc)
        logs['val_AU6_dum']=tot_acc
